5bkc8 |website=youtube.com |publisher=GMMTV |accessdate=27 March 2020 |language=Thai |date=22 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"font-style:italic;\" | In Time With You\n| ''TBA''\n| ''TBA''\n| \n|}\n\n===Music Video Appearances===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Song Title\n! Artist\n! Role\n! Notes\n|-\n|2013\n| ''Gawt Mai Dai (\u0e01\u0e2d\u0e14\u0e44\u0e21\u0e48\u0e44\u0e14\u0e49)'' \n| Bedroom Audio\n| Love interest\n| Official music video<ref>{{cite web |title=Bedroom Audio - \u0e01\u0e2d\u0e14\u0e44\u0e21\u0e48\u0e44\u0e14\u0e49 (Official MV) |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6bn533w3-M0 |website=youtube.com |publisher=CRISPY SOUND OFFICIAL |accessdate=31 March 2020 |date=3 December 2013}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2020\n| ''Tit Kap (\u0e15\u0e34\u0e14\u0e01\u0e31\u0e1a)''\n| [[Natthawut Jenmana]] (Max)\n| Sarawat\n| ''[[2gether: The Series (Thai TV series)|2gether: The Series]]'' Opening theme<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e15\u0e34\u0e14\u0e01\u0e31\u0e1a Ost.\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e23\u0e32\u0e30\u0e40\u0e23\u0e32\u0e04\u0e39\u0e48\u0e01\u0e31\u0e19 2gether The Series - \u0e41\u0e21\u0e47\u0e01\u0e0b\u0e4c \u0e40\u0e08\u0e19\u0e21\u0e32\u0e19\u0e30 |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQaI3VkSCi0 |website=youtube.com |publisher=GMMTV Records |accessdate=24 March 2020 |date=18 February 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| ''Khan Ku (\u0e04\u0e31\u0e48\u0e19\u0e01\u0e39)\n| Vachirawit Chivaaree (Bright)\n| Sarawat\n| ''[[2gether: The Series (Thai TV series)|2gether: The Series]]'' Ending theme<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e04\u0e31\u0e48\u0e19\u0e01\u0e39 Ost.\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e23\u0e32\u0e30\u0e40\u0e23\u0e32\u0e04\u0e39\u0e48\u0e01\u0e31\u0e19 2gether The Series - \u0e44\u0e1a\u0e23\u0e4c\u0e17 \u0e27\u0e0a\u0e34\u0e23\u0e27\u0e34\u0e0a\u0e0d\u0e4c |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=leevExpA8ec |website=youtube.com |publisher=GMMTV Records |accessdate=24 March 2020 |date=10 March 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n==Discography==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Year\n!Song Title\n!Romanized Title\n!